ComicInfo.Title: All Gave Some. Some Gave All.
ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Summary: All Gave Some. Some Gave All.: On Memorial Day, Storm Shadow and Stalker visit the memorial wall; Roadblock and Duke place flowers on the graves of the dead Joes; Hawk holds a ceremony at the Pit; Darklonian troops stakeout Sneak Peek's grave hoping to ambush Katya, but she outfoxes them; the Joes at Fort Wadsworth host a barbecue; Scarlett takes a lone ferry ride; at Snake Eyes' empty cabin, Timber howls at the moon.
